The role of Independent Judiciary is an essential element in achieving sustainable democracy in any democratic State. In establishing the imperativeness and indispensability of a fair and Independent Judiciary in a democracy, Sidne
y Brooks a United States Bankruptcy Judge succinctly posited in a presentation he made at a Fulbright Scholars Conference, April, 2007, saying 
\par "If it were left for me to decide whether we have a democracy without fair and Independent Courts or fair and Independent Courts without a democracy, I would not hesitate to choose the later".}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af39 \ltrch\fcs0 
