\par This was made obvious in Ekiti State, when the Speaker of the House of Assembly ostensibly ordered the Chief Judge of the State to dissolve the panel
 constituted by him because the panel was purportedly filled with people of questionable character. The Chief Judge refused and went ahead to inaugurate the panel. The members of the State House of Assembly ordered his suspension from office with immediat
e
